<PageTitle>BlazorNet11 Validation Demo</PageTitle>

<h1>Blazor .NET 11 Validation Demo</h1>

<p>This app demonstrates form validation with localization in a .NET 11 Blazor Server app.</p>
<p>Localization uses JSON files instead of .resx — via a custom <code>IStringLocalizerFactory</code>.</p>
<p>Use the navigation menu to go to the <a href="contact">Contact Form</a>.</p>
